4 A BILL FOR AN ACT ENTITLED: “AN ACT PROVIDING FOR A DRIVING PRIVILEGE CARD; ESTABLISHING
5 ELIGIBILITY, THE APPLICATION PROCEDURE, AND THE REQUIRED CONTENT FOR A DRIVING
6 PRIVILEGE CARD; PROVIDING FOR THE VOIDING AND REVOCATION OF A DRIVING PRIVILEGE CARD;
7 PROVIDING FOR THE ADOPTION OF FEES FOR A DRIVING PRIVILEGE CARD; PROVIDING
8 RULEMAKING AUTHORITY; PROVIDING DEFINITIONS; AMENDING SECTIONS 61-5-104, 61-5-105, 61-5-
9 110, 61-5-116, 61-5-121, 61-5-201, 61-5-203, 61-5-204, 61-11-503, AND 61-14-201, MCA; AND PROVIDING A
10 DELAYED EFFECTIVE DATE.”
