25 privilege card must be made on a form furnished by the department and be accompanied by the proper fee as
26 provided by rule.
27 (2) Each application must include the applicant's proof of identity, including full legal name, date of
28 birth, and sex, and THE APPLICANT'S proof of Montana residence.
